--- auth [feature] ---
AuthCont  [C]    : Authentication routes | $auth → THIS → AuthSer
AuthSer   [S]    : Authentication business logic | AuthCont ← THIS → AuthRepo ⇒ EvtAuthChanged
AuthRepo  [R]    : auth tables, RLS $tenant | AuthSer ← THIS → $db
AuthType  [T]    : Auth, CreateAuthDto, UpdateAuthDto
AuthVal   [V]    : Zod schemas for auth input | AuthCont ← THIS
AuthTest  [X]    : unit + integration tests
---
